Toogle Statusbar now uses the same function as the menu item
The Bookmark, Exit, Save As, Print Preview, Page Setup changed to use command instead of oncommand
Restart button correctly localized.
The About buttons for each application have been merged.
The Options, Addons, about:config and about:plugins now open in a tab in Thunderbird, if middle clicked.  Just like they already did in Firefox.
The Theme and Extensions button now work in Thunerbird 3.
Customize Toolbar button have been fixed in Thunderbird 3.
The resize text buttons have been fixed for Thunderbird 3.
